# Color files are runtime-generated by theme-switch (the sole writer). Ignoring
# them stops `chezmoi apply` from reverting the user's chosen theme back to the
# committed default. They are (re)generated on first apply by run_after_99-apply-theme.
.config/ghostty/colors
.config/waybar/colors.css
.config/fuzzel/colors.ini
.config/swaync/colors.css
.config/nwg-dock/style.css
# Whole stylesheets are token-rendered too now (shape + elevation, not only colour) — same sole-writer
# rule as the colour files: theme-switch owns them, so chezmoi must not revert them on apply.
.config/swaync/style.css
.config/fuzzel/fuzzel.ini
# ADL cohesion-base outputs (theme-switch is the sole writer; same rationale as the colour files).
.config/fontconfig/fonts.conf
.config/gtk-3.0/gtk.css
.config/gtk-4.0/gtk.css
.config/qt6ct/qt6ct.conf
.config/qt5ct/qt5ct.conf
.icons/default/index.theme
.config/archfrican/cohesion/vscode.colors.json
.local/share/archfrican-webapps-ext/theme.css
